.cursor/
.claire/
CLAUDE.md
_figma/
Form_Capstone/

## ── App-specific ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# User-uploaded files (profiles, documents, worksheets)
wwwroot/uploads/

# Keep upload folder structure if you add a .gitkeep later:
# !wwwroot/uploads/.gitkeep
